<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>wǒ men gēn zhe yì xiàng zǒu 迦南188</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men gēn zhe yì xiàng wǒ men yǒu le fāng xiàng
 nà jiù shì xiàng shì jiè xuān jiào jiāng fú yīn chuán biàn wàn bāng
 zhè shì wǒ men de shǐ mìng zhè shì wǒ men gòng tóng de yuàn wàng
 wǎn qǐ gāo shān dà hǎi jià qǐ fú yīn qiáo liáng,
 wǒ men gēn zhe yì xiàng zǒu, zhè cái shì wǒ men de fāng xiàng,
 wǒ men gēn zhe yì xiàng zǒu, jiāng fú yīn chuán biàn wàn bāng.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>188</hymn_number>
</song>